👥 Use case
AI-Assisted Retail Store Warranty Claim Triage & Resolution Assistant
Build a lightweight retail store application that helps store associates collect, validate, triage, and track customer warranty claim requests before escalation or approval.

The solution should help teams capture claims, identify missing proof of purchase or product evidence, classify claim severity, assign ownership, track status, generate reminders, and produce LLM-assisted resolution summaries and customer communication drafts.

Case Study
Customer Rajesh Kumar visits a retail electronics store requesting a warranty claim for a Bluetooth Speaker worth ₹8,000. During intake, the product, invoice, and a short description of the defect are provided, but warranty card details, serial number verification, and troubleshooting history are missing. The store associate uses the application to triage the claim, asks an LLM to summarize the case and draft a precise follow-up message, tracks pending information, sends reminders, validates submissions, and marks the claim as Ready for Manager Review.

